parameters: \n<Yuri> "You seem to be in a particularly bad mood today."

\n<Yuri> "There's no need to hide it. Just by looking at your
mouth, I can tell. It's more downturned than usual."
\n<Roselitte>"...Why don't you ask your own heart?"

\n<Yuri> "You... Even now, I'm surprised you can talk back to me
like that."

\n<Yuri> "...Ah, I see. It's because I brought alcohol, isn't it?
You're angry because I took alcohol on the expedition.
Right?"
Roselitte turned her face away with a huff.

\n<Yuri> "You're so uptight. It's not a big deal. It's not like
I'm planning to drink until I pass out."

\n<Roselitte>"...No, that's not it. I'm not angry about something like
that."
\n<Yuri> "Then why are you in such a bad mood?"

\n<Roselitte>"...This expedition mission. No matter if it was Lady Iris's
suggestion, isn't it unusual to leave not only the Royal
Guards but even me behind?"

\n<Roselitte>"But didn't we swear to each other? That no matter what
happens to me, I would serve by Your Highness's side. That
you would always keep me by your side."
\n<Roselitte>"...And yet, Your Highness did not take me with you."
\n<Roselitte>"Am I no longer able to fight for the empire?"
\n<Roselitte>"Can I no longer be of assistance to Your Highness?"

\n<Yuri> "Roselitte, bear with me a little longer... It should be
just ahead."
